name: Elvis Taylor
description: I am open and trusting until a person gives me a reason not to trust them and i believe integrity is important. I am looking for the same in a romantic partner and best friend. I am picky and won’t settle for anything but what i want and you shouldn’t either. I am looking for a friendship first and foremost. You know when there’s a spark. It’s what you do with that spark that determines if it becomes a passionate fire.
